---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms of use for PlainInfluence. Information about acceptable use, disclaimers, and limitations of liability."
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Terms of Use' }]}
>
  <section class="py-8 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Terms of Use</h1>
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-[var(--color-muted)] [&_h2]:text-[var(--color-foreground)] [&_strong]:text-[var(--color-foreground)]">
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> March 16, 2026</p>

        <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using PlainInfluence (plaininfluence.com), you agree to these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, please do not use this site.</p>

        <h2>Information Purpose</h2>
        <p>PlainInfluence is an informational resource that presents publicly available government data in a more accessible format. The information on this site is provided for general informational purposes only and should not be relied upon as professional advice.</p>

        <h2>Political Neutrality</h2>
        <p>PlainInfluence does not endorse, support, or oppose any political candidate, party, or organization. We present federal data as-is without editorial commentary or value judgments.</p>

        <h2>Accuracy and Completeness</h2>
        <p>While we strive to present accurate information, we make no warranties about the completeness, reliability, or accuracy of the data. Entity resolution (linking organizations across databases) may occasionally produce incorrect matches. Always verify important information with official government sources.</p>

        <h2>No Professional Advice</h2>
        <p>Nothing on this site constitutes professional advice of any kind — whether legal, financial, or otherwise. Any decisions you make based on information found here are solely your responsibility.</p>

        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>The underlying government data presented on this site is in the public domain. Our original design, code, text, and organization of the data are copyrighted by Kiznis.Studio.</p>

        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>This site may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.</p>

        <h2>Advertising</h2>
        <p>This site displays advertisements through Google AdSense to support its operation.</p>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, PlainInfluence and Kiznis.Studio shall not be liable for any damages arising from your use of or inability to use this site.</p>

        <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of any changes.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:hello@plaininfluence.com">hello@plaininfluence.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
